      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhoulinsheng/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2526995-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhoulinsheng/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大麦</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-25 15:30:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2954915_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  延续第一个本的风格，可是没有第一本说写的好。估计是因为牵涉到了现代史，抗日，解放战争。写的很教条。感觉在看教科书。基本上就是一带而过的。。希望看看世界史如何说吧。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2954915/#comments">(6回应)</a>
